  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A cozy adventure for hidden object lovers!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relax in a heartwarming atmosphere: find hidden items, solve puzzles & enjoy charming mini-games. Stroll in the garden, lounge by the pool, and host BBQs – every corner of your virtual home is full of warmth and secrets!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2701630/extras/990663095711093fbadb51de85ac5467.poster.avif?t=1772656901\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2701630/extras/990663095711093fbadb51de85ac5467.webm?t=1772656901\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2701630/extras/990663095711093fbadb51de85ac5467.mp4?t=1772656901\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collector’s Edition includes:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 exclusive cozy locations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beautiful desktop wallpapers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Soothing music player</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 bonus replayable mini-games</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2701630/extras/cdee82c7f8350dafeeb975276ae92567.poster.avif?t=1772656901\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2701630/extras/cdee82c7f8350dafeeb975276ae92567.webm?t=1772656901\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2701630/extras/cdee82c7f8350dafeeb975276ae92567.mp4?t=1772656901\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your perfect space filled with beauty and comfort. <strong>Welcome home!</strong></p>",
